<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        nav {
            display: flex;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        .avatar-container {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .avatar-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <nav>
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/about">About</a>
                <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
            </nav>
            <a href="/profile" class="avatar-container">
                <img src="<%= req.session.user.avatar %>" alt="User Avatar">
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Explore the World of Anime</h1>

        <p>Anime, a distinctive style of animation that originated in Japan, has captured the hearts of audiences worldwide. Known for its vibrant characters, compelling storytelling, and unique artistry, anime offers a diverse range of genres and themes.</p>

        <h3>Key Facts about Anime:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Anime encompasses various genres, including action, romance, fantasy, science fiction, and slice of life.</li>
            <li>Japan is the birthplace of anime, with its origins dating back to the early 20th century.</li>
            <li>Hayao Miyazaki, co-founder of Studio Ghibli, is renowned for creating critically acclaimed anime films like "Spirited Away" and "My Neighbor Totoro."</li>
            <li>"Astro Boy" (Tetsuwan Atom), created by Osamu Tezuka, is considered one of the first anime series, premiering in 1963.</li>
            <li>Anime conventions, such as Comiket in Tokyo, attract thousands of fans, showcasing cosplay, merchandise, and exclusive previews.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Explore the captivating world of anime, where imagination knows no bounds and storytelling reaches new heights. Whether you're a seasoned otaku or a newcomer, there's an anime waiting to enchant you.</p>
        <p>For some interesting animes to watch head to the about page</p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
